metadata.title: Wheel House Designs Women's Miniature Pinscher Socks
description: Wiggle your toes in comfort with our soft Miniature Pinscher socks. With a comfy blend of 75% acrylic and 25% stretch nylon, these dog socks will warm your feet and heart. Treat yourself to a pair, they also make a great Min Pin gift item. Ideal for everyday wear, the Miniature Pinscher socks are made to fit ladies size 9-11 or comparable sizes for men and children.
